snippet.title: Gift OST - Full Soundtrack by Cryo Interactive
snippet.description:
Hi, this is the complete soundtrack extracted from one of my favourite childhood games.

Track list & DOWNLOAD LINKS:
00:13 - 1. Title - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfRENBMFlyeW1aUW8/edit?usp=sharing
02:20 - 2. World Select - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfTVBsU0hnRGY0VTQ/edit?usp=sharing
04:51 - 3. Tipanic - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfR3hIUmxSazZubTA/edit?usp=sharing
07:13 - 4. Draculand - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfby1oeTdhRGVndzA/edit?usp=sharing
10:02 - 5. Paztec - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfcWd4X25PRkJNWHM/edit?usp=sharing
12:04 - 6. Star Stress - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfN3dXVm01TWZiVkE/edit?usp=sharing
14:27 - 7. Iceland - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfb2JQd0tIc3RMNlE/edit?usp=sharing
16:35 - 8. Mine - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfc0tCV3UwOUtLU2c/edit?usp=sharing
19:00 - 9. Alcatraz - https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxXwwH1nyfqfQ1AzLWJLUXV0SUU/edit?usp=sharing

Full game .exe here in polish:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1boXr_4apbM1-Eu-ZYFOV2ZJLWPbHKKBu/view?usp=sharing

Original CGI Gift Cartoon from 2004
https://www.youtube.com/@gift3418/videos

Please give me Like if you enjoy.
All rights belong to Philippe Ulrich and Cryo Interactive
